--------------------------- simple git server ---------------------------

install git instaweb
script to execute at each start with, e.g.:
crontab -e
@reboot /home/pi/startup_script.sh

#!/bin/bash
cd my_git_repo.git
git instaweb --httpd=webrick
cd /home/pi




